{"tid":635420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"環球時報總編用iPhone貼文：「抵制美國！支持中興！」","createTime":"2018-04-20T06:17:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T12:16:23.000Z","uid":28970,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"81af409e18c87e7d8be81786293a335915ea59c5","tid":635420,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:17:04.000Z","msg":"中美貿易戰爆發在即，近日美國商務部指 ZTE 中興通訊向伊朗等國家出售通訊設備，違反美國出口禁令而不加改善為由，對其實施 7 年期間的零件禁售，大廠如 Qualcomm 都不得向其供應晶片。事件令中國人民日報旗下《環球時報》總編胡錫進最近瘋狂貼文，呼籲中國人支持中興、抵制美國。不過他的微博帖文卻出賣了他，在帖文的日期旁邊，很明顯標示是從 iPhone 7 Plus 發出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/20/141516_a76160bcb3023d56e1537bfe37da0a62.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F20%2F141516_a76160bcb3023d56e1537bfe37da0a62.png&h=4e5e1388&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部宣布禁止美國公司向 ZTE 中興通訊出售零部件。事件令不少「愛國人士」憤慨，包括人民日報旗下《環球時報》的總編胡錫進。他在微博指美國商務部對中興下手，是因為害怕中國在 5G 上領先的發展勢頭，所以孤注一擲。又指「當年美國向中國賣程控交換機，每一部賺了我們多少錢！」。最後還呼籲中國人要支持中興，抵制美國。而胡錫進還在另一段發表的影片中指出，如果中美貿易戰全面打響，令中國人的生活受到影響，賬也要算到華盛頓的頭上。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/20/141538_40f9e515cf36d4422400e0290167c35c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F20%2F141538_40f9e515cf36d4422400e0290167c35c.png&h=db6903d7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/20/141539_a6fbf020513b2272440054def3848017.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F20%2F141539_a6fbf020513b2272440054def3848017.png&h=3cb9be6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過不少網友都發現了胡錫進這篇帖文有一個重大「漏洞」，就是帖文日期旁邊，標示了這篇文章是「來自 iPhone 7 Plus」。這件事情遭到中國網民的嘲笑，將已加上紅圈的截圖廣傳。<span style=\"color: red;\">有網民問他：「胡總，甚麼時候買華為手機？」，亦有網民問他「拿著蘋果但叫大家支持華為中興，要臉嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」</span>。有網民就很清醒，指 5G 的優勢根本不在中國，核心部件都掌握在別人手上，中國有何優勢可言？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/20/141553_bbcbb524bb9709ecc277965f71b2c377.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F20%2F141553_bbcbb524bb9709ecc277965f71b2c377.png&h=20146d82&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/20/141554_0b8ef7256da15d56ad7b5dcc2bb69ab0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F20%2F141554_0b8ef7256da15d56ad7b5dcc2bb69ab0.png&h=57c105fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前仍然有不少網民在胡錫進的微博留言，但他一於好少理，繼續發表「愛國」文章。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/04/19/zteiphone/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F04%2F19%2Fzteiphone%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=NITwp9Q6aaCxncUz4%2BDeoG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=24c750ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/04/19/zteiphone/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"914fbc5694bbbd7ff640ee7e414971c32e30a87e","tid":635420,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/20/141749_64a843ca1b52de50406531b91b470b3e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F20%2F141749_64a843ca1b52de50406531b91b470b3e.png&h=2dd4f8c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dad87dde98421975e389346c9d7a0c6abf5fe18","tid":635420,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:18:56.000Z","msg":"又係得個把口"},{"pid":"e